			<para>Find an equation whose solutions form the sphere of all points in <latex>\RNr[3]</latex> whose distance from the origin is equal to 3.</para>
		</problem>
		<approach>
			<answer><para><latex>x^2+y^2+z^2 = 9</latex></para></answer>
